@BloodBankManager_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000
@ContentType = application/json

### 1. GET All Blood Types
GET {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/bloodtypes
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### 2. POST - Create Blood Unit
POST {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/bloods
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "unitNumber": "U001",
  "bloodTypeId": 1,
  "collectionDate": "2026-03-12T10:00:00Z",
  "expiryDate": "2026-04-16T10:00:00Z",
  "volume": 450,
  "donorName": "Nguyễn Văn A",
  "location": "Kho A1"
}

### 3. GET All Bloods
GET {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/bloods
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### 4. GET Available Bloods by Type (FIFO)
GET {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/bloods/available/1
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### 5. GET Expiring Bloods (within 7 days)
GET {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/bloods/expiring/alert
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### 6. POST - Create Expiry Alerts
POST {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/bloods/create-expiry-alerts
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

### 7. POST - Create Patient
POST {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/patients
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "name": "Trần Văn B",
  "patientCode": "BN001",
  "bloodTypeId": 1,
  "dateOfBirth": "1990-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "gender": "Nam",
  "hospital": "Bệnh viện Lồi",
  "ward": "Phòng 101",
  "admissionDate": "2026-03-12T00:00:00Z",
  "phoneNumber": "0987654321",
  "email": "patient@example.com",
  "medicalCondition": "Chảy máu nội tạng"
}

### 8. GET All Patients
GET {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/patients
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### 9. GET Compatible Bloods for Patient
GET {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/patients/1/compatible-bloods
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### 10. POST - Transfuse Blood to Patient (with compatibility check)
POST {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/patients/1/transfuse
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "bloodId": 1,
  "quantity": 200,
  "performedBy": "Bác sĩ Nguyễn",
  "notes": "Truyền thành công"
}

### 11. GET Blood Inventory (Stock)
GET {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/bloodinventory
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### 12. GET Low Stock Alerts
GET {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/bloodinventory/low-stock/alert
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### 13. PUT - Update Low Stock Threshold
PUT {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/bloodinventory/1/threshold
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "newThreshold": 1500
}

### 14. GET All Expiry Alerts
GET {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/bloodexpiryalerts
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### 15. GET Active Expiry Alerts
GET {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/bloodexpiryalerts/active
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### 16. PUT - Acknowledge Expiry Alert
PUT {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/bloodexpiryalerts/1/acknowledge
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "acknowledgedBy": "Bác sĩ Nguyễn"
}

### 17. GET Expiry Alert Statistics
GET {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/bloodexpiryalerts/statistics
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### 18. PUT - Discard Blood Unit
PUT {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/bloods/1/discard
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "reason": "Hết hạn"
}

### 19. POST - Check and Mark Expired Bloods
POST {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/bloods/check-expired
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

### 20. POST - Refresh Alerts
POST {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/bloodexpiryalerts/refresh
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

### 21. GET All Payments
GET {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/payments
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### 22. GET Payment by ID
GET {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/payments/1
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### 23. GET Payments by Patient
GET {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/payments/patient/1
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### 24. POST - Create Payment
POST {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/payments
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "patientId": 1,
  "amount": 500000,
  "paymentMethod": "Cash",
  "description": "Thanh toán cho máu A+",
  "status": "Completed"
}

### 25. PUT - Update Payment
PUT {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/payments/1
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "patientId": 1,
  "amount": 600000,
  "paymentMethod": "Credit Card",
  "description": "Thanh toán cập nhật",
  "status": "Completed"
}

### 26. DELETE - Delete Payment
DELETE {{BloodBankManager_HostAddress}}/api/payments/1
